-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cage-the-elephant@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cage-the-elephant@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cage-the-elephant">Cage The Elephant</a>主唱马特·舒尔茨 (Matt Shultz) 公开讲述了他面临的“心理健康危机”，正是这场危机导致他于 2023 年被捕。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/cage-the-elephant-social-cues-review-2478026">将大象关在笼子里——“社交线索”评论</a></strong></li></ul><p>去年1月，舒尔茨因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cage-the-elephants-matt-shultz-arrested-for-criminal-gun-possession-3376261">非法持有两把上膛的枪而</a>被捕，此前曼哈顿下城包厘街酒店的一名员工据称看到他携带一把手枪进入底层公共厕所。</p><p>检察官称，舒尔茨当时似乎喝醉了，当警察到达他的酒店房间时，他们发现了两把枪和一组 11 张宝丽来照片，其中一些照片显示了涉案枪支。</p><p>他后来承认了三项罪名：企图刑事持有武器、刑事持有枪支和刑事持有武器，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cage-the-elephants-matt-shultz-avoids-jail-for-criminal-gun-possession-3451288">达成免入狱认罪协议</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3376262" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3376262" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3376262" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Matt-Shultz-of-Cage-The-Elephant.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="《笼中大象》的马特·舒尔茨。图片来源：蒂姆·莫森菲尔德（Tim Mosenfelder），盖蒂图片社" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Matt-Shultz-of-Cage-The-Elephant.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Matt-Shultz-of-Cage-The-Elephant.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Matt-Shultz-of-Cage-The-Elephant.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Matt-Shultz-of-Cage-The-Elephant.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Matt-Shultz-of-Cage-The-Elephant.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Matt-Shultz-of-Cage-The-Elephant.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3376262" class="wp-caption-text"> 《笼中大象》的马特·舒尔茨。图片来源：蒂姆·莫森菲尔德（Tim Mosenfelder），盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>现在，舒尔茨终于通过 Instagram 上的帖子公开了这起事件。 “我今天能站在这里真是一个奇迹。去年我被捕了，这无疑救了我的命。被捕后，我住进了医院两个月，然后又接受了几个月的门诊治疗。我终于可以解释发生了什么，”他写道。</p><p>这位歌手解释道：“在过去的三年里，我不知不觉地在与一场彻底的心理健康危机作斗争。在很短的时间内，由于对我开的药物的医源性反应，我陷入了精神病。”</p><p>他接着说，正是通过朋友、家人、乐队成员和妻子的爱，他才得以度过难关。他谈到了妻子“坚定不移的爱”和支持，并表示她的支持“加上专业治疗帮助我重新掌控现实并完全康复”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C36Q_txOy9n/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(